# API / Server Rules

Express TypeScript server in `apps/raincloud/server/`. API-only (no UI serving). Main: `apps/raincloud/server/index.ts`.

## Routes & auth

- Routes in `apps/raincloud/server/routes/`
- Auth middleware: `apps/raincloud/server/middleware/auth.ts`
- Main API: `apps/raincloud/server/routes/api.ts`

## Swagger

Update `apps/raincloud/server/swagger.ts` when adding/changing API endpoints.

## Tests

Add tests in `apps/raincloud/server/__tests__/` and `apps/raincloud/server/routes/__tests__/`.
